With Galvanax's defeat, all finally seems to be safe in Summer Cove.

and is still after the Ninja Nexus Prism! Luckily the Rangers are

and awesome Megazords made from legendary super ninja steel. Together,
the Power Rangers fight an epic battle to save the galaxy from destruction!
